      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COMPTON ROCKY (3) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, hitting the frame latest when 2nd at this track over 732m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Deserves serious consideration. OREGON JANET (5) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 3.5 lengths at this track in a handy 43.81. Jumping from the pinch draw but goes well at this distance. Can make it two on the bounce. NITRO NEO (1) finds it hard to win but has a consistent overall record, having placed 52 of 102 career runs. Has hit the frame at his last three runs, the latest finishing third (44.49) at this track. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Racing well and deserves a win. ZENVO YOYO (7) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
